4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer". This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge in the field and aims to help them start a career as a data scientist. The course duration is 16 weeks and includes 3 classes per week. The class size is limited to a maximum of 12 people.

The course covers a wide range of topics including Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Participants will learn to create predictive models using popular libraries such as Pandas and Numpy. They will also explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, and work with supervised and unsupervised learning models.

In addition to theoretical knowledge, participants will have the opportunity to practice solving real-life cases and gain hands-on experience with industry-standard tools. They will also learn to strategize and develop their own AI projects, covering the entire lifecycle from development to deployment and maintenance while ensuring privacy and security.

No previous experience is required to enroll in this course, and participants can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. Live classes will be taught in the language of the campus.

Upon completion, participants will receive a certificate recognized by multiple organizations. For more information, visit the [4Geeks Academy website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop